<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وهو تقدم برقم <span class="c2">(١٥٦٣)</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٧٢)</span> -<span class="c5"> (حديث:</span> <span class="c1">" اعرف وكاءها وعفاصها "</span> <span class="c2">(ص ٤٦٤)</span> .<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
